{"id": 1962, "genre": 1000, "title": "游戏角色要显得活生生，你觉得哪些元素比较重要？", "description": "比起只会说“这事不归我管”的人类办事员，有些游戏里的 npc 还要更有人情味一点。", "record_count": 11365, "comment_count": 18, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171017153333Hqh5a31YNM29RugL.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-10-18T17:00:33Z", "questions": [{"id": 3139, "title": "游戏角色要显得活生生，你觉得哪些元素比较重要？", "content": "游戏角色要显得活生生，你觉得哪些元素比较重要？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 242167, "content": "故事线丰满，比如有家庭，死后身上有给家人的信", "image": "img/option/option/201710171601006MJCqzSY2n04QVNG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242168, "content": "有日常生活，比如怪物会聚在一起烤火聊天", "image": "img/option/option/20171017161728iRjtr8XaGfuUQgAb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242170, "content": "有缺陷，比如可能会走神、结巴、害怕承诺、自私…", "image": "img/option/option/20171017164932GOUi81KaLB7Sqlnc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242169, "content": "操作不输玩家，可能还会偷袭啥的", "image": "img/option/option/201710171617437CxytEwdOf3cAq4u.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242172, "content": "难以预测，战术有变化、发挥也可能时好时坏", "image": "img/option/option/20171017162131J5MpmyujvlbUhx74.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242175, "content": "会有一些具有个人特征的小动作设计", "image": "img/option/option/20171017170746bGLjHcWaVZoF92we.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242174, "content": "会吐槽、抬杠，比如史坦利寓言里的旁白", "image": "img/option/option/20171017171421X8MWFTEfNdcIh1sp.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 242177, "content": "甚至能意识到自己是游戏里的人，氛围秒变科幻片", "image": "img/option/option/20171017165051DcRhswXpdTvJy7B8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}